*gnumeric-1.6.0 (29 Oct 2005)

  29 Oct 2005; Joe McCann <joem@gentoo.org> +gnumeric-1.6.0.ebuild:
  New version of gnumeric. Cleaned up ebuild, remove libgda support(requires
  dev version), and update deps. Removing other archs until goffice has the
  proper keywords. Closes bug #108969

